# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# EAS Build Archive Exclusions
# EAS only needs the Expo/React Native JS source + assets.
# Everything else (Python ML backend, training data, server, deps) is excluded.
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── Git repository history (19 GB — biggest culprit) ──────────────────────
.git/

# ── Python ML backend (largest contributor — PyTorch venv alone is ~5 GB) ──
ml/

# ── Node.js backend (separate server, not needed for APK) ──────────────────
server/

# ── npm / Node dependencies (rebuilt on EAS servers) ──────────────────────
node_modules/
**/node_modules/

# ── Expo / Metro build outputs ──────────────────────────────────────────────
.expo/
dist/
web-build/
android/
ios/
.metro-health-check*

# ── YOLO / ML model weights ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.pt
*.onnx
*.engine
*.weights
*.keras
*.h5
*.tflite
*.pb

# ── YOLO training run artifacts ─────────────────────────────────────────────
runs/

# ── Backup folders ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
MODELS_BACKUP_*/

# ── Python cache / bytecode ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
__pycache__/
**/__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd
*.egg-info/

# ── Credentials & secrets (never upload) ────────────────────────────────────
firebase-service-account.json
*.keystore
*.p12
*.pem
.env
.env.*
server/.env

# ── Build artefacts & logs ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.apk
*.aab
*.ipa
*.log
*.gz
*.tar
*.zip

# ── Dev-only scripts & docs ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
start-ngrok.ps1
screenshots/
docs/
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.ps1
*.bat
*.sh

# Git internals
.git/